uman ACE2s. Finally, two polymorphous Rhinolophous sinicus bat ACE2s showed different susceptibilities to virus entry by RaTG13 and SARS-CoV-2 S pseudovirions, suggesting possible coevolution. Our results offer better understanding of the mechanism of coronavirus entry, host range, and virushost coevolution.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Li, Pei", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Guo, Ruixuan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Liu, Yan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhang, Yingtao", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hu, Jiaxin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ou, Xiuyuan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mi, Dan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chen, Ting", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mu, Zhixia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Han, Yelin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chen, Zihan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Cui, Zhewei", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhang, Leiliang", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wang, Xinquan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wu, Zhiqiang", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wang, Jianwei", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jin, Qi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Qian, Zhaohui", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/23a606ede6e79295888c9c51c18ed66a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/8aea8128fc3ebb782799e43f2e9e1f57edf134e16e32c5fbdfc572f197602ffb", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/UKCGFW9A", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/UKCGFW9A", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/f8f95b00337c21e686081e166cfc8b97!/b373502-376048", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPart